## 11. Accessibility Requirements

| Requirement | Implementation |
|-------------|---------------|
| Keyboard navigation | All interactive elements reachable via Tab; Enter/Space activates |
| Screen reader | `aria-label` on all SVG elements; `role="img"` with descriptions |
| Colour contrast | All text meets WCAG AA (4.5:1 minimum) |
| Motion reduction | `prefers-reduced-motion` media query disables non-essential animations |
| Font scaling | Rem-based font sizes; no fixed px text |
| Focus indicators | Visible 3px purple focus ring on all interactive elements |
| Audio subtitles | All narration has simultaneous text display |

