## 15. Risks & Mitigations

| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|-----------|--------|------------|
| Audio autoplay blocked by browser | High | Medium | Require click-to-start on intro screen; all content works muted |
| localStorage unavailable (private browsing) | Low | Low | Graceful fallback; session-memory-only mode |
| Large audio files slow initial load | Medium | Medium | Lazy-load audio per scene; show loading indicator |
| SVG simulation lag on older tablets | Low | High | Throttle animation to 30fps on low-perf devices via `requestAnimationFrame` |
| LMS API downtime | Low | Low | Non-blocking submission; local retry queue |

